reviews: I love this hat. It improved my looks (said my wife). I have worn the hat for two hot summers. There are vents in the hat permitting a wonderful airflow over your (my nearly bald) head. No head sweat marks It is a tough hat. Do not spend time in rain with it on. I will acquire another should I lose it.
product_name: Dorfman Pacific Co. Men's Rush Gambler

reviews: The hat is well made and looks great. I have a huge melon so I ordered the XL size even though I was nervous that it would still be too small. As it turns out it fit pretty darn well, if not just a tad on the big side which is OK. You will not be disappointing with the quality of this hat.
product_name: Dorfman Pacific Co. Men's Rush Gambler

reviews: Best buy I have made this summer ... I should of bought it earlier when it was still warm and sunny out (I live in Canada). It's super light, fits nice and comfy on your head, looks good too ... Definitely worth it!! And the shipping was super quick as well!!
product_name: Dorfman Pacific Co. Men's Rush Gambler

reviews: I love this hat, I wore it all summer and suspect it will serve me well for another season or two. It is pretty low, though, so it rides high on my head. That took some getting used to and it isn't much good in windy weather. After a particularly sweaty day it fit much better, so I suspect if you soak it in hot water and wear it while it dries it might form to my head. Haven't actually tried that yet. I like it, but if you have a high pointy head it might not fit well. ;-)
product_name: Dorfman Pacific Co. Men's Rush Gambler

reviews:
I ordered this for my trip to Mexico. Honestly, I hardly took it off the entire time I was there.
The construction is pretty good. The hat has great shape too.
My only complaint is the lack of a strap to hold it to your head. It was really noticeable when I was on the beach with the wind blowing.
I think I will make holes and add my own strap for use at the beach back home.
product_name: Dorfman Pacific Co. Men's Rush Gambler

reviews:
It a big hat for a big head.

so if you want it to stay flat this may not be for you.
